{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is going to happen to me if the police comes and this and that, and that I will be found guilty?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the guy jumped out from the car that I rear ended.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, I want to introduce myself to you right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My name is Jerome Cohen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was from Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He spoke with a French accent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a French reporter by the name of Jerome Cohen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I knew Cohen would not hurt me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the outcome of my visit to the Olympics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't exactly remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the-- It was an ice skating event.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I didn't see as many events, really, as I mingled with the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were so hungry to get out of our ghetto existence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that was really what prompted me to do this, that-- that it was just-- I felt good in just being amongst normal people who-- who were not marked people, who were not ghettoized.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Munich, and everywhere, we really ghettoized in the fact that we couldn't go to the park.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were all over signs-- Jews are not wanted here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we went-- there was a very small selected places, a few places-- I was still traveling for my father's business at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were very few places where we could go to hotels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had signs out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews are not wanted here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you came, you were subject to prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I had no papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember that-- while I was still in Germany, our passports that we had previously were taken away from us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to hand in our passport so that we could not leave the country without getting our passports back.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
